imdb.plot outline: The soup opera shows the daily life of children in third grade at Mundial school. Helena Fernandes is a young and beautiful teacher who carries a lot of love. As his first actual work, enters at Mundial School to teach the class of the third year. Using affection, peace and hepatic she conquers all her students. Outside the school, the children form a club called "Patrulha Salvadora" where they gather in an abandoned house. They help their classmates and other children who do not study in school.
imdb.title: Carrossel
